    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Annual Reports</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          The Annual Report is published each April just before the Annual Parish Meeting which is usual held in May. It
          summarises the activities of the Parish Council for the year. At Annex A you can find the summary of the
          accounts for the financial year ending 31 March for each year.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Please click on the links below.</p>
        <div class="my-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024-25</h3>
          <ul class="my-4 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/annual-reports/2024-25/notice-of-exercise-of-public-rights-2025.pdf" target="_blank">Notice of Exercise of Public Rights 2025</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/annual-reports/2024-25/annual-report-2024-25.pdf" target="_blank">Annual Report 2024-25</a>
            </li>
            <li>
